Class AbstractRepository<T,ID>

Object
AbstractRepository<T,ID>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of entity this repository works with
ID - The type of the entity's identifier
All Implemented Interfaces:
Repository<T,ID>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ApplicantRepository, ApplicationRepository, EnquiryRepository, ManagerRepository, OfficerRepository, ProjectRepository, RegistrationRepository
public abstract class AbstractRepository<T,ID> extends Object implements Repository<T,ID>
Abstract repository implementation that provides common functionality for serializing and deserializing objects to/from files.
